data.description: INTERIOR JUST FULLY PAINTED! Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home spanning 1954 sqft. Enjoy an open living space, accentuating the inviting atmosphere. The sunroom provides a peaceful retreat, and the large back deck is perfect for outdoor gatherings. Keep your vehicles protected in the 2-car garage, and utilize the bonus storage shed for added convenience. This home offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality for your needs. Come and experience it today!
